A New Day
I rise with the sun,
A crisp morning unfolding,
In the stillness of air.
As the dew drops waken,
And new flowers embrace the day.

With each gentle whisper
As light penetrates the night,
I feel the warmth ignite,
Creating new colors of joy,
In the canvas of life.


- Langston Hughes
